&lt;li&gt;You will be working with hardware engineers to create firmware and software for the hardware being designed with hardware and deliver functionality for the platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will own the delivery of your code from end-to-end, automating continuous integration and delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
