&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive hourly wage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stock options&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive health benefits (medical, dental, vision) for employees and qualified dependents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Healthcare spending accounts (FSA, HSA)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401K retirement plan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Up to 20 weeks of parental leave&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible PTO policy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
